{"tid":2482841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭去年減薪「共度時艱」　1年後即追加8%至月薪42萬","createTime":"2021-04-10T10:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T08:49:21.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"62478ac28cc22a33b089fa5bfac87bf02f26f4b7","tid":2482841,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T10:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201130/410100269322342400098256.jpeg/AtZl68oKxFRf0rOqDeCXuOA9gT46M169-v1ptPr9abQ?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201130%2F410100269322342400098256.jpeg%2FAtZl68oKxFRf0rOqDeCXuOA9gT46M169-v1ptPr9abQ%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=3df621ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官辦公室今日（9日）向立法會提交文件，披露相關薪酬津貼。特首林鄭月娥2021至22年度的薪金為508.02萬元，非實報實銷酬酢津貼為98.24萬元。以此計算，林鄭平均月薪約42.34萬元，較上年度的39.08萬元增加3.26萬元或8.3%。<br />\n<br />\n其實林鄭2020至21年度原訂薪金521萬元，平均月薪為43.4萬元，但由於新冠疫情爆發，為了與市民共度時艱，林鄭宣佈減薪10%至468.96萬元，平均月薪39.08萬元。<br />\n<br />\n不過，本港疫情仍未過去，經濟及就業情況持續低迷，3月中失業率更升至7.2%，而林鄭就率先追回減薪幅度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNS8mAi8YpdYop6QM7iKGYktr6fFqxGqpH6ek8qELoCcM?filename=jLeX720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjLeX720.jpg&h=51cacc2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55270a65c349542bf003bdcfafa0df7930f380ff","tid":2482841,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:49:21.000Z","msg":"有冇back pay先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}